  <!-- ==================== WEARABLES / META GLASSES ==================== -->
  <section id="wearables" class="relative py-28 md:py-36 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(139,92,246,0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">

      <!-- Section header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16 space-y-5">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-purple-500/20 bg-purple-500/5 text-xs font-semibold text-purple-400/80">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-400 animate-pulse"></span>
          Coming Soon &mdash; Pending App Store Approval
        </div>
        <h2 class="reveal text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
          CARAPACE for<br>
          <span style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa 0%, #8b5cf6 50%, #7c3aed 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">Meta Glasses</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="reveal text-base text-white/35 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Imagine your AI agent living in your glasses. No phone in hand. No screen to look at. Just you, the world, and an AI that sees everything you do.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal text-sm text-white/25 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          We’ve built the Meta wearables SDK integration. It’s ready. We’re awaiting Meta’s SDK approval to ship it through the App Store. In the meantime — we’re giving beta access to our first 500 iOS users.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature highlights -->
      <div class="reveal grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mb-16">
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 text-center space-y-3">
          <div class="text-3xl">👓</div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Always-On Context</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/35 leading-relaxed">Your AI sees through your glasses continuously. No activation, no unlock. It’s just there.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 text-center space-y-3">
          <div class="text-3xl">🎙️</div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Whisper-to-Agent</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/35 leading-relaxed">Talk quietly. Your agent listens, processes through your OpenClaw gateway, and responds in your ear.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 text-center space-y-3">
          <div class="text-3xl">🔒</div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Still Your Data</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/35 leading-relaxed">Everything routes through your private OpenClaw gateway. Meta doesn’t see your conversations.</p>
        </div>
